<div class="post"><div class="posttop"><div class="username">Zedd</div><div class="date">December 11th, 2004, 11:54 AM</div></div><div class="posttext">OK I will try and be as coherent as possible, but I am pretty pissed at this point.<br />
<br />
Timeline:<br />
<br />
Approx Nov 26 I left a phone message with Diamond Relocations of Canoga Park, CA that I was interested in hiring them as my mover.  I had picked them from several quotes I'd received because they seemed reliable, and offered to do it for the best price.<br />
<br />
Sunday Nov 28 (they work on Sundays) I was emailed a quote:<br />
